Metadata: Washington Sea Grant Invests in Washington: Program Highlights 2020
program reports (annual, progress, planning reports, etc)

Washington Sea Grant (WSG) invests in a range of marine programs supporting four focus areas in Washington State: Sustainable Fisheries and Aquaculture, Healthy Coastal Ecosystems, Resilient Communities and Economies, and Ocean Literacy and Workforce Development. Below is a sampling of programs and recent activity: our-year program evaluation - WSG successfully completed a program-wide evaluation, which is conducted every four years by the National Sea Grant office at NOAA.
